Author: x24throwaway
Text: When I realised I was only eating one meal a day and exercising for hours, religiously, is when I realised I had an ED.

Author: IDKijustdrinkhere
Text: Honestly, I have no idea. I can only look back and realize it was disordered. I guess somewhere in my 20s but I was 15 when it actively started. Although, I can remember being 5 or 6 and knowing I was skinny and loving it. I use to chug water on an empty stomach and shake so I could hear it slosh around in my empty stomach. So fucking weird now that I think back on it.
